1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=Detik Aku Bertemu Awak=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:15,000
=Episod 1=

3
00:00:22,775 --> 00:00:25,312
(Mao Buyu, Civet Lord)

4
00:00:26,839 --> 00:00:28,280
Mao Buyu, Civet Lord.

5
00:00:29,760 --> 00:00:32,119
Kau bersembunyi dalam
Embroidered Guard bertahun-tahun.

6
00:00:32,280 --> 00:00:33,679
Kau berkhidmat untuk Baginda.

7
00:00:34,600 --> 00:00:36,759
Negara dilanda
penyamun kebelakangan ini.

8
00:00:37,039 --> 00:00:38,320
Sebagai komander,

9
00:00:39,119 --> 00:00:40,439
kau turut bertanggungjawab.

10
00:00:40,840 --> 00:00:44,880
Kau diarahkan menyamar di
Kementerian Kehakiman sebagai konstabel.

11
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:48,320
Kau mesti tangkap ketua buruan terkenal,
Jade Squirrel.

12
00:00:48,960 --> 00:00:50,640
Gerak-geri pencuri itu sukar dijangka.

13
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:52,640
Dia ancaman besar
kepada istana diraja.

14
00:00:53,159 --> 00:00:54,399
Risikonya amat tinggi.

15
00:00:54,640 --> 00:00:56,960
Jangan bocorkan identiti kau
sebagai Embroidered Guard.

16
00:00:57,240 --> 00:00:57,840
Patik akan

17
00:00:58,960 --> 00:00:59,600
menjunjung perintah.

18
00:01:00,700 --> 00:01:02,862
(Kediaman Mao)

19
00:01:05,159 --> 00:01:05,799
Buyu!

20
00:01:06,159 --> 00:01:06,760
Buyu...

21
00:01:07,159 --> 00:01:07,760
Ayah!

22
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:09,040
Kau budak nakal!

23
00:01:09,040 --> 00:01:11,319
Kau betul-betul jadi ejen penyamaran
untuk Gate Bureau!

24
00:01:12,519 --> 00:01:13,079
(Mao Wenrong, Ketua Konstabel, Unit Risikan)
Buyu!

25
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:14,000
Buyu!

26
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:15,840
Pengarah Liu.

27
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:16,560
(Pengarah Personel, Liu Sanhuai)
Buyu.

28
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:18,359
Pesuruhjaya Luo menandatangani dekri.

29
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:19,280
Mulai hari ini,

30
00:01:19,640 --> 00:01:21,480
kau rasmi menjadi
konstabel Gate Bureau.

31
00:01:22,319 --> 00:01:23,920
Buyu, aku dah tahu.

32
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:26,760
Aku tahu kau takkan puas
jadi pemalas jalanan selamanya.

33
00:01:26,959 --> 00:01:28,280
Kau dah ubah hidup kau.

34
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:30,200
Warisan keluarga Mao kini di tangan kau.

35
00:01:32,159 --> 00:01:32,719
Tengok, Buyu.

36
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:34,920
Seragam konstabel kau ada di sini.

37
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,760
Ayah, Pengarah Liu,

38
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:39,760
Saya baru teringat
sesuatu yang sangat penting.

39
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:41,640
Saya kena uruskan sekarang juga.

40
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:42,200
Ayah, jangan...

41
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,040
Jangan risau!

42
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:44,120
- Aku akan balik!
- Buyu!

43
00:01:44,130 --> 00:01:45,852
- Kau nak pergi mana?
- Buyu! Kau nak ke mana?

44
00:01:45,984 --> 00:01:47,870
(Kedai Bunga Yunchang)

45
00:01:50,512 --> 00:01:53,462
(Chu Yunchang, Jade Squirrel)

46
00:01:57,719 --> 00:01:58,120
Chang!

47
00:01:58,239 --> 00:01:58,719
Alamak.

48
00:01:58,920 --> 00:01:59,760
Aku cedera.

49
00:02:00,719 --> 00:02:01,400
Biar aku tengok.

50
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:02,840
Teruk mana?

51
00:02:04,959 --> 00:02:05,719
Zhizhi!

52
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:08,560
Cepat, ambil ubat
sebelum calar Buyu sembuh sendiri.

53
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:10,520
Apa yang bawa kau datang?

54
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,800
Aku datang nak beritahu berita baik.

55
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:15,280
Aku dah rasmi jadi konstabel
Gate Bureau.

56
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,000
Apa?

57
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:21,680
Mulai sekarang, takkan ada orang
berani ganggu kau lagi.

58
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:25,360
Chang,

59
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,080
Aku nak kau jumpa ayah aku.

60
00:02:27,879 --> 00:02:28,599
Jumpa ayah kau?

61
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:32,280
Aku nak ayah aku
meminang keluarga kau.

62
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:40,560
(Zhizhi, Poison Master)
Tak sangka kau ada, Mao.

63
00:02:41,439 --> 00:02:42,199
Tak ada apa.

64
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,840
Aku patut pergi dulu.

65
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:45,840
Hati-hati.

66
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:49,240
Dunia ni kenapa?

67
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,560
Tak sangka Buyu
masuk Gate Bureau.

68
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:52,719
Kak,

69
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,360
Aku rasa kau sebenarnya bertuah.

70
00:02:55,439 --> 00:02:56,439
Mula-mula

71
00:02:56,439 --> 00:02:58,560
kau terserempak
dengan lelaki bahaya macam tu.

72
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,719
Kau nak buat apa?

73
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,199
Kau masih

74
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:03,240
nak jumpa ibu bapanya
petang ini?

75
00:03:04,039 --> 00:03:05,190
Mungkin kau patut batalkan saja.

76
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,680
Aku mesti pergi.

77
00:03:07,199 --> 00:03:08,080
Mestilah aku pergi.

78
00:03:08,150 --> 00:03:09,280
Jadi kalau dia konstabel pun kenapa?

79
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,280
Tak ada apa nak ditakutkan.

80
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:11,919
Bukannya

81
00:03:11,919 --> 00:03:13,800
seluruh keluarganya konstabel.

82
00:03:14,837 --> 00:03:15,737
(KETUA-KETUA KONSTABEL)

83
00:03:15,900 --> 00:03:17,250
(TIADA PENCURI DI BAWAH LANGIT)

84
00:03:18,159 --> 00:03:19,360
(Aku dah habis.)

85
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:21,719
(Semua keluarga Buyu
ketua konstabel.)

86
00:03:22,719 --> 00:03:25,080
(Aku macam masuk sarang musuh.)

87
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,000
Chang,

88
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,159
(Mao Jixian, Ketua Unit Siasatan)
ini ayah aku.

89
00:03:27,439 --> 00:03:28,960
Dia Ketua Unit Siasatan
di Gate Bureau.

90
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,840
Salam, Ketua Mao.

91
00:03:31,639 --> 00:03:32,639
Ini kakak aku,

92
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:35,120
Mao Wenrong dari
Unit Risikan Gate Bureau.

93
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,439
Hai, Kak Rong.

94
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,960
Dan ini abang ipar aku,

95
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:42,400
(Xu Anran, Ketua Koroner)
Xu Anran, Ketua Koroner.

96
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:43,439
Cik Chu.

97
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,080
Jaga hal sendiri.

98
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,520
Cik Chu,

99
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:49,120
sebenarnya kerja apa untuk cari makan?

100
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:50,479
Saya urus kedai bunga.

101
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:52,240
Perniagaan kecil saja,

102
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:54,400
tapi cukup untuk tanggung saya

103
00:03:54,599 --> 00:03:55,199
dan Buyu.

104
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:56,840
Cik Chu,

105
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:59,520
keluarga Mao
keturunan konstabel.

106
00:03:59,919 --> 00:04:03,120
Semua ahli, lelaki atau wanita,
berkhidmat di Gate Bureau.

107
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,000
Ajaran keluarga jelas.

108
00:04:05,159 --> 00:04:07,000
Kalau orang Mao nak berkahwin,

109
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:09,599
pasangannya juga mesti
daripada Gate Bureau.

110
00:04:10,159 --> 00:04:10,800
Faham?

111
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:15,360
Ayah, jangan terlalu keras.

112
00:04:15,479 --> 00:04:16,480
Buyu,

113
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:18,720
sebagai orang Gate Bureau,

114
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,720
aku harap kau kahwin

115
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:21,480
dengan wanita yang ada kaitan Bureau.

116
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:23,240
Dia boleh sokong kau,

117
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:25,040
faham kau, dan bantu kau.

118
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:27,120
Biar kau fokus selesaikan kes

119
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,920
tanpa risau urusan rumah.

120
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:30,279
Habis, cinta macam mana?

121
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:32,399
Cinta boleh dipupuk.

122
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,720
Tengok kakak aku.

123
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,800
Ayah paksa dia kahwin dengan Anran.

124
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:36,680
Aku tak nampak

125
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:37,920
banyak cinta antara mereka.

126
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:38,839
- Kau ni!
- Kau!

127
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:39,720
Sayang,

128
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,480
makanlah buah.

129
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,560
Kenapa kau fikir

130
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,920
aku dan suami aku tak bahagia?

131
00:04:45,399 --> 00:04:46,720
Sayang, makan buah.

132
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:48,360
Cepat makan!

133
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,120
Ya.

134
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:50,920
Kak,

135
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,040
cukup-cukuplah.

136
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,120
Lakonan kau teruk.

137
00:04:53,279 --> 00:04:55,120
Apa pun, aku takkan setuju

138
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,720
kau kahwin dengan wanita yang bukan

139
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,360
orang Gate Bureau.

140
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,240
Selagi aku masih hidup, jangan harap!

141
00:05:00,279 --> 00:05:01,399
Ayah, tolonglah.

142
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:04,480
Jangan cakap yang bukan-bukan.

143
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,560
Chang, awak nak jumpa saya?

144
00:05:17,399 --> 00:05:18,720
Keluarga awak tak suka saya.

145
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,900
Saya tak nak membebankan awak.

146
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,360
Kita patut berpisah.

147
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,560
Itu saja keyakinan

148
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,600
awak pada cinta kita?

149
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,639
Walau kita tak bersama,

150
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,720
kita masih boleh berkawan.

151
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:33,560
Macam mana nak berkawan saja
dengan gadis yang saya cinta pandang pertama?

152
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:39,279
Awak kena bertenang.

153
00:05:42,199 --> 00:05:42,839
Chang,

154
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,040
Saya dah jatuh cinta pada awak

155
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,279
sejak kali pertama nampak awak.

156
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,839
Saya takkan lepaskan awak.

157
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,560
Dan jangan cakap begitu lagi.

158
00:05:49,959 --> 00:05:51,079
Awak takkan menyesal?

159
00:05:51,759 --> 00:05:53,720
Apa pun yang berlaku,

160
00:05:54,079 --> 00:05:55,199
awak takkan berputus asa dengan saya?

161
00:05:55,279 --> 00:05:56,160
Takkan.

162
00:05:56,839 --> 00:05:58,759
Saya dah beritahu ayah saya.

163
00:05:59,519 --> 00:06:00,790
Bila saya selesaikan kes besar,

164
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,639
saya akan kahwini awak.

165
00:06:03,759 --> 00:06:04,839
Bukan semudah itu.

166
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,399
Dulu memang susah.

167
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:07,959
Tapi sekarang,

168
00:06:08,399 --> 00:06:09,160
yang saya perlu cuma

169
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,639
tangkap penjenayah buruan

170
00:06:10,639 --> 00:06:11,279
Jade Squirrel.

171
00:06:14,519 --> 00:06:15,959
Jade Squirrel?

172
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:17,839
Biar saya beritahu,

173
00:06:17,839 --> 00:06:18,959
si tupai itu kunci kita

174
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:21,079
untuk hidup bersama.

175
00:06:21,519 --> 00:06:22,600
Saya kena pergi kerja.

176
00:06:22,959 --> 00:06:24,399
Nanti saya cari awak dalam beberapa hari.

177
00:06:29,519 --> 00:06:30,279
(Bodoh.)

178
00:06:30,959 --> 00:06:33,720
(Haiwan yang awak buru itu saya.)

179
00:06:38,500 --> 00:06:41,275
(Ratu Pencuri, Chu Xiangling)

180
00:06:41,519 --> 00:06:42,839
(Raja Pencuri, Mei Guangzu)
Pedupaan Sembilan Naga Pasangan Kekasih.

181
00:06:43,079 --> 00:06:45,600
Ini pusaka keluarga
terkaya di ibu kota.

182
00:06:45,839 --> 00:06:47,160
Nilainya sangat besar.

183
00:06:49,279 --> 00:06:50,279
Sekarang tengok ini.

184
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,600
Mutiara Penangkis Habuk.

185
00:06:51,959 --> 00:06:52,959
Kalau simpan ini pada diri,

186
00:06:52,959 --> 00:06:53,959
awak akan kekal bersih

187
00:06:53,959 --> 00:06:55,639
walau berjalan seribu li.

188
00:06:55,639 --> 00:06:56,759
Ini memang harta berharga.

189
00:06:57,279 --> 00:06:58,319
Bagus, sayang.

190
00:07:03,639 --> 00:07:04,439
Mak Cik, Pak Cik.

191
00:07:04,620 --> 00:07:05,519
Bukankah kita dah janji?

192
00:07:05,519 --> 00:07:06,639
Tak boleh mencuri lagi.

193
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:07,720
Saya...

194
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:09,199
Kami bukan mencuri.

195
00:07:09,639 --> 00:07:11,399
Kami cuma beri pengajaran sikit

196
00:07:11,399 --> 00:07:13,279
pada pencuri kecil di kawasan kita.

197
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:13,839
Betul.

198
00:07:13,839 --> 00:07:14,639
Cukup dengan alasan.

199
00:07:14,759 --> 00:07:15,759
Mencuri tetap mencuri.

200
00:07:16,279 --> 00:07:16,839
Er...

201
00:07:16,959 --> 00:07:18,600
Baiklah, baiklah. Takkan berulang lagi.

202
00:07:18,639 --> 00:07:19,959
Sekali ini saja, ya?

203
00:07:20,959 --> 00:07:21,600
Chang,

204
00:07:21,839 --> 00:07:22,759
Saya dengar

205
00:07:22,759 --> 00:07:24,879
awak jumpa ibu bapa Mao Buyu hari ini.

206
00:07:26,279 --> 00:07:26,959
Apa

207
00:07:26,959 --> 00:07:28,639
kerja keluarga Mao?

208
00:07:28,839 --> 00:07:30,519
Ayah suruh kamu berdua buat kerja.

209
00:07:30,519 --> 00:07:31,839
Kenapa balik lambat sangat?

210
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:34,439
Sebenarnya Mao Buyu buat kerja apa?

211
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:35,120
Cepatlah, beritahu.

212
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:36,680
Beritahu!

213
00:07:42,439 --> 00:07:43,759
Apa rahsia besarnya?

214
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,279
Ayah,

215
00:07:45,519 --> 00:07:46,720
Buyu terlalu naif.

216
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:48,759
Dia pun belum semak latar belakang dia,

217
00:07:48,959 --> 00:07:50,439
tapi dah nak rancang hidup dengan dia.

218
00:07:50,839 --> 00:07:51,879
Ayah tak boleh biarkan.

219
00:07:52,439 --> 00:07:53,319
Rong,

220
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:55,720
tak ke kita agak terlalu keras

221
00:07:56,079 --> 00:07:57,720
pada Chu Yunchang?

222
00:07:58,199 --> 00:07:59,199
Apa yang kau cakap?

223
00:08:00,639 --> 00:08:02,839
Kita baru jumpa dia sekali.

224
00:08:02,839 --> 00:08:03,959
Kita tak betul-betul kenal dia,

225
00:08:04,199 --> 00:08:05,439
tapi kita terus tolak dia.

226
00:08:05,639 --> 00:08:07,279
Tak hairan Buyu melawan.

227
00:08:07,279 --> 00:08:09,279
Kalau dia bukan dari Gate Bureau,

228
00:08:09,519 --> 00:08:10,959
dia tak layak dalam keluarga ini.

229
00:08:11,959 --> 00:08:13,319
Itu mungkin betul,

230
00:08:14,639 --> 00:08:16,480
tapi kita perlukan alasan kukuh

231
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:18,000
untuk yakinkan Buyu.

232
00:08:18,712 --> 00:08:19,775
(Kedai Bunga Yunchang)

233
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:21,759
Ini tempatnya?

234
00:08:21,759 --> 00:08:22,759
Ketua Mao!

235
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:23,639
Ketua Mao!

236
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:25,519
Apa?

237
00:08:25,879 --> 00:08:27,639
Inilah kedai bunga
yang Buyu selalu pergi.

238
00:08:32,399 --> 00:08:34,039
Hati-hati, bunga itu ada duri.

239
00:08:34,039 --> 00:08:34,600
Tak apa.

240
00:08:40,159 --> 00:08:41,759
Nampak? Saya dah cakap.

241
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:44,360
Hari ini hari jadi awak.

242
00:08:44,639 --> 00:08:45,759
Beritahu apa yang awak nak,

243
00:08:46,519 --> 00:08:47,279
saya akan berikan.

244
00:08:47,879 --> 00:08:49,480
Awak tak takut duri saya?

245
00:08:49,879 --> 00:08:52,000
Saya tak kisah,
walau awak kaktus sekali pun.

246
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:59,000
Ayah? Kakak?

247
00:08:59,519 --> 00:09:01,039
Apa ayah buat di sini?

248
00:09:01,639 --> 00:09:02,879
Kami cuma lalu sini.

249
00:09:03,759 --> 00:09:04,759
Kami singgah sekejap.

250
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,399
Ketua Mao. Rong.

251
00:09:06,879 --> 00:09:07,639
Silakan masuk.

252
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,759
Jadi, ini kedai awak?

253
00:09:11,159 --> 00:09:11,639
Rong,

254
00:09:11,639 --> 00:09:13,240
kalau ada yang berkenan,

255
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,279
anggap saja percuma.

256
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:14,879
Tak ada.

257
00:09:16,879 --> 00:09:17,639
Yunchang,

258
00:09:18,039 --> 00:09:19,879
siapa lagi dalam keluarga awak?

259
00:09:38,519 --> 00:09:39,879
Biar aku perkenalkan semua orang.

260
00:09:40,159 --> 00:09:41,519
Ini mak cik saya,

261
00:09:41,639 --> 00:09:42,759
dan ini pak cik saya.

262
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:44,879
Gembira berkenalan.

263
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,159
Hai, semua.

264
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:47,759
Kenapa mak cik dan pak cik awak

265
00:09:48,159 --> 00:09:49,279
tak guna pintu depan?

266
00:09:50,639 --> 00:09:52,279
Ini tradisi keluarga

267
00:09:52,279 --> 00:09:53,399
ambil jalan yang pelik.

268
00:09:53,399 --> 00:09:54,759
Lagipun, bagus untuk bersenam.

269
00:09:54,759 --> 00:09:55,620
Sambil menyelam minum air.

270
00:09:55,639 --> 00:09:56,519
Tepat sekali.

271
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:57,860
Bagus untuk kesihatan.

272
00:09:57,879 --> 00:09:58,759
Ya.

273
00:10:02,639 --> 00:10:04,399
Ini ayah Buyu,

274
00:10:04,399 --> 00:10:05,759
dan ini kakaknya.

275
00:10:07,759 --> 00:10:09,360
Ketua Mao. Cik Mao.

276
00:10:09,879 --> 00:10:12,759
Ketua Mao, apa hajat tuan hari ini?

277
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,039
Begini, saya...

278
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:18,159
Hari ini hari jadi Chang,

279
00:10:18,879 --> 00:10:21,480
jadi saya bawa ayah untuk berkenalan.

280
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:26,039
Saya cuma nak kahwin dengan Chang.

281
00:10:26,090 --> 00:10:27,399
Ayah saya makin risau,

282
00:10:27,399 --> 00:10:28,879
jadi dia nak jumpa kamu berdua.

283
00:10:30,759 --> 00:10:32,039
Faham. Kalau begitu,

284
00:10:32,639 --> 00:10:33,399
silakan masuk.

285
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:37,519
Tunggu, kami belum sedia apa-apa.

286
00:10:37,759 --> 00:10:38,639
Sedia apa?

287
00:10:38,639 --> 00:10:41,639
Ada apa dalam rumah ini yang kamu sorok?

288
00:10:41,639 --> 00:10:42,519
Tak!

289
00:10:42,799 --> 00:10:44,399
Kebanyakan benda di sini elok disorok.

290
00:10:47,519 --> 00:10:50,000
(Satu keluarga konstabel jumpa keluarga buruan.)

291
00:10:50,799 --> 00:10:51,519
(Yunchang,)

292
00:10:51,879 --> 00:10:53,159
(inilah ujian paling getir kau.)

293
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:56,390
(Kita tak boleh biar semuanya musnah hari ini.)

294
00:11:03,187 --> 00:11:06,462
♪Dendam dan sesal umpama arak yang kuat♪

295
00:11:06,512 --> 00:11:09,387
♪Teguk saja, lalu lepaskan♪

296
00:11:09,662 --> 00:11:15,380
♪Cawan kosong untuk cinta dan benci kita♪

297
00:11:16,860 --> 00:11:20,180
♪Air mata mengabur takdir yang tak mampu kuatur♪

298
00:11:20,180 --> 00:11:23,100
♪Mari minum sampai fajar♪

299
00:11:24,100 --> 00:11:29,340
♪Di sebalik topeng ini, aku takkan berdusta♪

300
00:11:30,787 --> 00:11:33,180
♪Setiap pertemuan semula terasa seperti pertama kali♪

301
00:11:33,180 --> 00:11:36,830
♪Senyum tersembunyi ini takkan pudar♪

302
00:11:36,900 --> 00:11:40,390
♪Satu hati, tetap di sisimu♪

303
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:43,575
♪Hingga ke hujung waktu♪

304
00:11:43,625 --> 00:11:46,862
♪Bulan melakar wajahmu♪

305
00:11:46,937 --> 00:11:50,662
♪Diselimuti awan, kau penuhi hatiku♪

306
00:11:50,820 --> 00:11:57,060
♪Mencari dirimu
dan menepati janji selamanya♪

307
00:11:57,125 --> 00:12:00,340
♪Doa sunyi dalam jiwaku♪

308
00:12:00,637 --> 00:12:04,175
♪Mendukung ikrarku di bawah bulan♪

309
00:12:04,487 --> 00:12:07,512
♪Berharap kita takkan terpisah lagi♪

310
00:12:07,512 --> 00:12:10,612
♪Menuju selamanya♪

311
00:12:10,650 --> 00:12:14,500
♪Bulan melakar wajahmu♪

312
00:12:14,500 --> 00:12:17,860
♪Diselimuti awan, kau penuhi hatiku♪

313
00:12:18,220 --> 00:12:24,180
♪Mencari dirimu
dan menepati janji selamanya♪

314
00:12:25,100 --> 00:12:34,740
♪Hanya untuk bersamamu♪

